== Welcome to WeatheredWatcher 

This is my personal website, written in Ruby on Rails.  Besides the obvious, telling folks a bit about me, this site is kind of a breeding grounds for a bunch of fun, playfull stuff that I am doing in Ruby!

So far, I've got only a few really cool things here to look at.

1) I am using Posterous for my blog...but I also wanted it displayed nativly, so to speak, here.  I used some ruby to parse an rss feed and display it on a well formed blog page.
2) I am trying not to use flash or anything that might hurt my HTML Strict status!  So I have a custom feed 